WEBVTT

00:01.437 --> 00:02.386
There are two kinds of folks

00:02.443 --> 00:04.043
who sit around thinking
about how to kill people:

00:04.377 --> 00:06.103
Psychopaths
and mystery writers.

00:06.341 --> 00:07.363
I'm the kind that pays better.

00:07.764 --> 00:09.503
Who am I?
I'm Rick Castle.

00:09.593 --> 00:10.653
Castle.
Castle.

00:10.688 --> 00:12.388
I really am ruggedly handsome,
aren't I?

00:12.442 --> 00:14.632
Every writer needs inspiration.
And I found mine.

00:14.842 --> 00:15.661
Detective Kate Beckett.

00:15.908 --> 00:17.175
Beckett.
Aah!

00:17.448 --> 00:19.533
Beckett?
Could you get some backup, please?

00:19.884 --> 00:21.768
<i>And thanks to my friendship
with the Mayor,</i>

00:21.819 --> 00:23.453
<i>I get to be on her case.
Oh!</i>

00:23.487 --> 00:26.056
Do I look like a killer to you?
Yes, you kill my patience.

00:26.090 --> 00:27.724
<i>And together,
we catch killers.</i>

00:28.272 --> 00:31.174
I hate this case.
I know. Isn't it great?

00:33.930 --> 00:35.467
♪ Oh, God, baby ♪

00:35.567 --> 00:37.735
♪ can't you see ♪

00:37.802 --> 00:39.237
♪ I'm lonely without you? ♪

00:39.304 --> 00:41.105
♪ I'd go crazy ♪

00:41.173 --> 00:43.674
♪ if you leave ♪

00:43.742 --> 00:45.776
♪ I'm nothing without you ♪

00:45.844 --> 00:48.478
♪ I've been trying ♪

00:48.547 --> 00:50.480
♪ to move on ♪

00:50.549 --> 00:52.950
♪ I've been trying... ♪

